#: symfexit/payments/models.py:160 symfexit/payments/models.py:194
msgid ""
"Assets and expenses are increased with debits, decreased with credits. "
"Liabilities, equity, and income are increased with credits, decreased with "
"debits. Tick this if the account increases with credits. This makes sure the "
"balance is shown correctly."
msgstr ""
"Activa en kosten nemen toe met debet, af met credit. Passiva, eigen vermogen "
"en inkomsten nemen toe met credit, af met debet. Vink dit aan als de "
"rekening toeneemt met credit. Dit zorgt ervoor dat het saldo correct wordt "
"weergegeven."

#: symfexit/payments/models.py:165
msgid "general ledger"
msgstr "grootboek"

#: symfexit/payments/models.py:220
msgid "Accounts Receivable"
msgstr "Debiteuren"

#: symfexit/payments/models.py:222
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Accounts receivable represents money owed by entities to the firm on the "
"sale of products or services on credit. In RGS this is mapped to BVorDebHad "
"(13011). See: {rgs_url}"
msgstr ""
"Debiteuren vertegenwoordigt geld dat entiteiten verschuldigd zijn aan de "
"organisatie voor de verkoop van producten of diensten op krediet. In RGS is "
"dit gekoppeld aan BVorDebHad (13011). Zie: {rgs_url}"

#: symfexit/payments/models.py:240
msgid "Revenue"
msgstr "Omzet"

#: symfexit/payments/models.py:242
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Membership revenue balance account. In RGS this is mapped to WLbeLbvLbv "
"(82811). See: {rgs_url}"
msgstr ""
"Balansrekening voor lidmaatschapsomzet. In RGS is dit gekoppeld aan "
"WLbeLbvLbv (82811). Zie: {rgs_url}"

#: symfexit/payments/models.py:260
msgid "Waived Payments"
msgstr "Kwijtgescholden betalingen"

#: symfexit/payments/models.py:262
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Expense account for waived (forgiven) payment obligations. When a payment is "
"waived, the debt is written off against this account. In RGS this is mapped "
"to WBedVkkAdd (45661). See: {rgs_url}"
msgstr ""
"Kostenrekening voor kwijtgescholden (vergeven) betalingsverplichtingen. "
"Wanneer een betaling wordt kwijtgescholden, wordt de schuld afgeboekt tegen "
"deze rekening. In RGS is dit gekoppeld aan WBedVkkAdd (45661). Zie: {rgs_url}"

#: symfexit/payments/models.py:281
msgid "Bank"
msgstr "Bank"

#: symfexit/payments/models.py:283
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Bank account (rekening-courant). In RGS this is mapped to BLimBanRba "
"(10201). See: {rgs_url}"
msgstr ""
"Bankrekening (rekening-courant). In RGS is dit gekoppeld aan BLimBanRba "
"(10201). Zie: {rgs_url}"

